{"tid":1192784,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"同我講警察係善良唔係黑警？","createTime":"2019-06-08T15:06:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-08T18:29:07.000Z","uid":41389,"like":17,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3ace6b199e6f3b493869e2ec6df03f27f6e272c6","tid":1192784,"uid":41389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T15:06:18.000Z","msg":"同話林奠個閪唔係臭有咩分別？<br />\n屌你老母成班毅進仔選擇性執法 過分暴力 淨係識郁手<br />\n係善良就唔會當差啦 <br />\n警察唔係維護政權唔通幫香港人呀？<br />\n慈母手中棍咋 兇鳩人最叻 <br />\n三毛又傾到新策略<br />\n<br />\n__________________<br />\n<br />\n-遊行起點：銅鑼灣維多利亞公園中央草坪 （維園草地）<br />\n-遊行路線：維園草地起點&gt;高士威道&gt; 禮頓道&gt;伊榮街&gt;邊寧頓街&gt;軒尼詩道西行車路&gt;金鐘道&gt;樂禮街&gt;夏愨道&gt;添美道&gt;立法會外行人路終點<br />\n-集合時間：2：30PM<br />\n-起步時間：3：00PM（或維園草地達八成滿）<br />\n-衝定唔衝，自己執生<br />\n-記得宗旨：不散<br />\n<br />\n溫和：<br />\n<strong>【長期置頂】69反送中遊行須知整合</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1191837/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1191837/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>[懶人包] 第一次參加遊行的常見疑問Q&amp;A</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1186623/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1186623/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>【極重要】69遊行記得帶防Rfid卡套</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1190797/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1190797/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n勇武： <br />\n<strong>食放題須知，全部資料，一世受用</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1191403/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1191403/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>[law撚］被捕人仕須知</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1189300/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1189300/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>［抗爭手冊］End game前準備</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1169374/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1169374/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">黑色三毛警告信號現正生效 6月8日16時</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">表示連登 facebook 網絡廣泛地區已錄得或預料會有每秒三毛回覆量超過70次/禁70次正評的網絡分化攻勢，且攻勢可能持續或於今晚或明朝早上升級。</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VNv7C24.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVNv7C24.jpg&h=73f7da13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">注意事項</span></strong></span><br />\n<strong>網民應注意username 同 三毛開post 目的 而非三毛post正評數量。<br />\n網民應負皮三毛post 入去屌佢老母 而毋須參與分化討論。<br />\n鍵盤戰士應努力推正經post 例如準備時項去抵擋三毛攻勢。<br />\n三毛會開一啲反共post 減低大家戒心 請細心思考現時網絡上所有言論。<br />\n一般市民應少上連登 關電視 而休養等待明天遊行。<br />\n鬼得一隻 林奠 其他完全唔重要 。</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZB4gyv7.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZB4gyv7.gif&h=7cacc0df&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b8a4eb662d7aa2181fb0531b25e10e704b0cd69f","tid":1192784,"uid":52230,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T15:06:58.000Z","msg":"呼籲勿同情敵人<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>槍口一致對外！<br />\n<br />\n不要分化！不要懷疑隊友！<br />\n<br />\n有人被捕立即群擁而上集體救援！<br />\n<br />\n勿比機會警犬單獨拉走同伴！<br />\n<br />\n一切行動必須群體出發！ <br />\n<br />\nStick Together Team! 不要落單！<br />\n<br />\n6.9 GOGOGO!</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>唔衝嘅人幫手拖住篤灰狗 <br />\n<br />\n衝嘅巴繼續上前！<br />\n<br />\n齊心！</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b74261d37db5be0a65ba4c618b8144fa43fd0d4a","tid":1192784,"uid":148987,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T15:07:03.000Z","msg":"七警<br />\n警棍扑頭<br />\n胡椒<br />\n告女人胸襲警察<br />\n猶太人集會<br />\n濫捕<br />\n夾口供"},{"pid":"dac770a14e31b61933f0bd3cb780d7cbb4818287","tid":1192784,"uid":143033,"lik